dialogue.subtitleText: Help me fight for this zone, will ya?

dialogue.subtitleText: I'm in contested zone. Help appreciated

dialogue.speaker: c3d5371f-3b65-4a7a-a999-d0e6285f6b95
dialogue.subtitleText: Hey! Zone contested on my position.

dialogue.speaker: c3d5371f-3b65-4a7a-a999-d0e6285f6b95
dialogue.subtitleText: Core is mine. Need a hand here.

dialogue.speaker: c3d5371f-3b65-4a7a-a999-d0e6285f6b95
dialogue.subtitleText: They are now under my protection.

dialogue.speaker: c3d5371f-3b65-4a7a-a999-d0e6285f6b95
dialogue.subtitleText: Stay outta my line of fire!

dialogue.speaker: c3d5371f-3b65-4a7a-a999-d0e6285f6b95
dialogue.subtitleText: Screw you! We lost one of our own

dialogue.speaker: c3d5371f-3b65-4a7a-a999-d0e6285f6b95
dialogue.subtitleText: Not a bad kill, but no class. Haha!

dialogue.speaker: c3d5371f-3b65-4a7a-a999-d0e6285f6b95
dialogue.subtitleText: Oh, I'm gonna take my time with you!

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Ouch! Someone's going to need some medgel after this race.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: I don't know how many more hits like that they can take.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And that's why in racing we have the saying, "ships don't win pretty."

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: After a crash like that, these pilots have got to be asking, "Did I remember to give my welder a gift last Citizen Day?"

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Now that's what I call a bang up job.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: While crashing into the other pilots may stop them from winning, it often has the adverse affect of causing you to lose as well.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: These pilots are not holding back.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: They clipped! Hopefully they can maintain control.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: They're bumping each other like they're at a club on Terra Prime.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: I don't know the exact maths, but I am fairly certain that two objects hitting at these speeds is equal to about a metric ton of uh-oh.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Get ready. Things are about to get lethal.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Heading into the final stretch and it still could be anybody's race. Well not anybody's. Some of these pilots are not very good.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: We got one lap remaining, and one last chance for these pilots to prove themselves.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: It's the final lap, and here is where you start to see just how good these pilot's engineering crews are, as the ships have been taking a beating.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And with that lap, the end draws near.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: The qualifier is winding down as we start the last lap.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: It all comes down to this last lap.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Final lap. Time for things to get interesting.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Racers are entering the final lap.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: This is the beginning of the end! The Last lap! The final bow! The ultimate circle. The big... okay I ran out of things but you get the idea. The race is almost over.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Last lap and time to use whatever they got left in the tank.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: With the season rapidly approaching, it'll be interesting to see who, if anyone, really establishes themselves as a racer to watch.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: With Kale Sonora's qualifier win at Issigon last week, everyone's asking if any of today's competition will knock her out of the top slot.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Couldn't argue for better conditions to race in, I suppose. Call me old-fashioned, but I follow the Waylon Vickers mantra: "I love it when the weather's an opponent."

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: New Horizon is really proving itself to be a thinking man's racetrack.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: My understanding is that Consolidate Outlands owner, Silas Koerner, is enjoying the race today from his luxury box. Let me just say, Silas, if you are on the market for a new best friend, I am available.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: The MCRs recently implemented enhanced saftey protocals are on full display. Sure it makes the race a little less exciting, but I guess some people would argue that's worth the price of saving some lives. Not me persay, but some people.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: I can't believe I'm watching this!

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Dealing with the sheer difficulty of this New Horizon course is a common theme in these Murray Cup qualifiers.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: For those of you watching who are interested in getting involved with Murray Cup racing, it really comes down to two things, practice, and a ton of credits to buy a ship.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Dealing with stress and fatigue may almost be as important in a race like this as is the ship you fly.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Little known fact, this raceway was designed from the ground up to make these pilots gently weep to themselves as they fly.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: This course is not one you want to fight against. The best bet is to close your eyes and just go along for the ride.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: It's hard to imagine what those original Murray Cup racers, using planets to mark the course, would think of today's track innovations.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: It really is austounding how there seems to be no one way to win this race. Having the fastest ship means nothing if you're going to get your ass blown off.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: One of the great things about Murray racing is how the debate over speed vs. agility vs. firepower vs defense still rages to this day.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: I'm reminded of a similar race in 2938 where all the ships also went around a track very fast.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: New Horizon, a recent edition to the Cup, has been devisive amongst pilots as they strive to master all its nuances.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Hard to believe that there was a time when the Murray Cup was just a cup owned by a guy named Murray.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: You'll often hear people grunting over max engine output, but give me precise maneuvering thrusters any day.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Today's race is turning out to be a real stick breaker.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Many of the pilots have switched from drinking water during the race to a hydrating gel, just to shave off those few precious grams from their ships weight.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: With barely meters to spare, these rings pose a significant risk to ships at these intense speeds.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Big risk there. We'll have to see if they made their move a little too early.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: That's when you know the ships are really handling well, when they can pull a ring like that and manage to hold the line.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: To the pilots in this race I ask, can you go faster? And if yes, then please, go faster.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: New Horizon Raceway known throughout the circuit for its tricky turns and of course its new horizons.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: With a race track this huge, it can sometimes be difficult for pilots to get a full handle on the pacing they need to set for themselves.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: As an announcer it is important that I remain impartial, however as a race fan I got to say, I hope someone crashes soon.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Seems we have a contrarian in the race.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Race fans, we may be moments away from a crash, as a pilot with no regards for their own life or the lives of others, flies in the wrong direction.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: This is so incredibly dangerous but I will not turn away.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Someone's helmet must be too tight because they are flying backwards.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: As a pilot heads in the wrong direction, we are once again reminded that drug screening has still yet to be perfected.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: We have one pilot going the wrong way round the track, so it may be worth specifying that the direction in which you cross the finish line does in fact matter.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And... now there is a pilot flying in the wrong direction.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Attention to the pilot going the wrong way, you are going the wrong way.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Watching this ship fly the wrong way, you have to ask, are they pre-screening these pilots?

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Pilots are ready at the gates.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Ships are at their start positions.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Pilots getting ready to launch. Can't say enough how important a good start is to a racer.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: The wait is almost over as the ships are primed.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Last chance to make final adjustments as we are near the start.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Pilots are in place, and the ships are set.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Racers are lined up and ready to go.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Mechanics are making the final adjustments before we get underway.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Ships are at the line, and you can feel the excitement.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Engines hum and thrusters burn as they wait for that final count.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Faster, harder, and better than ever. Whether you're describing this Murray Cup's season, or me, your host Trevor Basque, you'd be right. Welcome to the New Horizon Qualifiers.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: We are back and racing in New Horizon. Im Shawn Walker for GSN Murray Cup coverage.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: You can feel the excitment here at New Horizon as we gear up for another Murray Cup race. I'm Shawn Walker, and welcome to the Qualifiers.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Hello ladies and gentlmen, welcome to the New Horizon Speedway in lovely Ellis System for another Murray Cup Qualifier.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Do you feel that? That need to feel g-forces pull blood from your brain? Well, look no further. Racing season is back.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: This is Trevor Basque for Murray Cup racing. Let's go now to today's qualifier.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Hello everyone, this is Trevor Basque, got another surefire heartstopper about to get underway.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome to the Murray Cup Qualifier, my name's Trevor Basque.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Hello racers and gearheads, this is Trevor Basque casting live from the New Horizon Raceway.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: If you've got Murray Cup fever, then you've come to the right place. I'll be your doctor, Trevor Basque, but instead of a cure, I'll be dosing out just more racing fever, or something. I am not a real doctor. On to the race!

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome back to Murray Cup racing. Hello, I'm Trevor Basque and let's go straight away to today's qualifier.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Lets see if the pilots will be making adjustments as they head into the next lap.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And around we go for another lap.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Unlike Synthworld, that lap is done.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And the ships clear a lap.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Clearing a lap, you've got to wonder if this is the point where racers will begin to make their move.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: With that lap done, this is where strategy is really going to start coming into play.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And the Qualifier is kicked off.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And a clean launch out of the gate.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Controlling these ships at speeds this high is no easy task, as another pilot slips outside the track.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: What is going on here? They're off the track!

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Looks like we have a rebel, who's not going to be penned in by your racing lines.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: That racer went wide... real wide... off the track wide.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Those racing guides are there for a reason, you know.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Can someone please make sure the pilots know how racing is supposed to work?

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: They're flying like a Jumpers fan after a match. Incapable of going in a straight line.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: With the trouble these pilots are having staying on the course, you might suspect that they don't actually want to be in the race.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Anyone want to nudge them back on course?

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Out of the danger zone, looks like there's still a handful of competitors.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: As pilots are eclipsed by their competitors, you can really tell who's got what it takes, and who's got to get their resume into shape.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: That's either a rough bit of luck, or a great bit of luck, dependant, of course, on who you are cheering for.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: It's make or break time, and some of these pilots are just plain broken.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: That could be it, that could be the decisive turn of this race.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: A qualifier as important as this, it's so important to keep your head in the game.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Falling behind. Not something you want to do in races or in taxes for that matter.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Use it or lose it, and that pilot clearly chose lose it.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: That pilot's got some work to do to make up for lost ground.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: There you go, lose focus for even a second, and another pilot is there to pick up the slack.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: That is going to be a costly mistake.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: You've got to ask how a pilot could just give up their position like that.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Some clear gains being made as racers settle in.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: That is one pilot who's got to be pleased with themselves.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And that racefans, is why nothing's settled till the finish line is crossed.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: That was a surgical move right there to slip past their competition.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Cutting in line, rude at the souk, perfectly acceptable on the raceway.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: We've got movement in the pack as a racer slips ahead.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: We've got a change in position and a reminder that nothing is certain till they cross that final line.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: A pilot overtakes the competition, and gamblers everywhere sweat a little bit more.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: We've got a pilot making their move.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Some expert handling as a pilot advances.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Aggressive flying on full display at New Horizon today.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: We are nosecone to nosecone as these pilots try desperately to find some more speed.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Neither of these pilots seems ready to let go of the lead.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Who's it gonna be? Who's it gonna be?!?

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: With a race this close, I bet these pilots are regretting not removing that bobblehead from the dash.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: This is unbelievable. These two competitors are absolutely refusing to give up that edge.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: It's a battle for the ages.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: They are really jockeying for position.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: This is looking like it's going to be too close to call.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: These racers seemed determined to not give each other any breathing room.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: In Murray Cup racing, the ships are fast, but the guns are often faster.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: YES! Yes! That was a marvelous shot. If the race continues like this, not sure how much longer my voice will last.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Shots are fired and the competition is thinned.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: It was a battle for the ages, but someone had to go down in flames.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: A warning shot fired across the bow, or rather, straight into it.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Have I said recently how grateful I am they added guns to this sport?

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: The real trick here is maintaing target lock, while not letting up on the throttle.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: We're seeing some real offensive flying. No love lost here.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Pick your shots. Everyone hates spray and pray. So undignified.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Some pilots, really having an off race. They may want to rethink any plans to buy a lottery ticket today.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: We are seeing lots of ships struggling to get a hold of this track today.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: As the race goes on, pilots are really beginning to fade.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: To those of you thinking of becoming pilots, this race should be considered a prime example of how not to win races.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: At this level of competition, seeing flying this shoddy is almost a rare treat.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Some pilots try to win through pure speed, others with percision, and by the looks of it, we have a few pilots out there trying to win through a new strategy I'm going to dub, "being awful."

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: This... this is just dreadful flying.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: The pack is really starting to seperate.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Looks like some of the pilots have chosen to hang back and avoid the whole 'struggling to win' all together.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: There are so many drivers in the rear of this pack who have just not had opportunity yet to show what they can do.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: The pilots leading this race have to be wondering, is this the time to play it cautious, or is it the time to really go for it?

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: It is astounding that these pilots have been able maintain this pace.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: There is some exemplary flying happening here today. A real treat.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Everything is looking neat and tidy as these pilots show off why they are the best in the empire.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: I have never seen anything like this. This is a clinic of precision and skill.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: The competition is being absolutely dominated right now.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: The leader is simply outmatching everyone. It's like they're on a whole other level.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: There are no guarantees in Murray Cup, but this race is starting to look like a sure thing.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: If I've said once, I've said it a hundred times. Perfecting the foundations of racing will always dominate tech.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: I encourage these pilots to use today's results as an opportunity for some serious soul searching. Is racing really what I am meant to do?

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: With results like these... there's always next year, I suppose.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Well, the one thing you get say about that race is at least it's finally over.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: That race may be best described by my old Equivalency instructor when she said, "there's room for improvement."

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: The sound and the fury has come to an end, and all we are left with is a lot of depressed pilots.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Congratulations to the winners. Condolences to the losers. And to those in the middle... I got nothing.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: With over 500 years of Murray Cup racing history, I can firmly say that this race was most certainly, pretty inconsequential.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: There you have it, another mediocre race comes to a bland conclusion, and I die a little inside.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: (Yawns). Hmm? Oh, it's finished? Someone's supposed to wake me before the end of the boring ones.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: "What an exciting finish!" is something I wish I could say. Instead I am forced to go with, "That race was certainly something that happened."

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: If ever there was a time for the death threats against me to come to fruition, let it be now, 'cause racing does not get much better than that my friends.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Did everyone just see that?!? And people wonder why I constantly scream, "I love racing!"

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Start to finish, that was a well executed race.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: After watching that performance, it may be safe to say that we could be looking at our next Murray Cup champion.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And across the line! That has got to be one pilot who is pleased with themselves.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: What a finish! I think we may have just witnessed the making of a legend.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: That race, ladies and gentleman, will be the new thing I picture while making love to my wife.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Remember where you were this day race fans. You're grandkids are going to be asking about it.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Done! I'm calling it! It's over! Not just this race! But all racing ever! That's how good that finish was. They didn't just win a race, they won racing itself.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: People ask how we're ever going to make peace with the Vanduul and I say make them watch a race like that. I'll be damned if seeing flying that good doesn't make everyone just want to hug it out.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And it's over. If you need to cry, please, go ahead. It's not a reasonable reaction, but I'm afraid it's a natural one after a race like that.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: A heartfelt congratulations to the winner, and a scornful shake of the head for the loser.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: It is rare to see a beating this bad outside of an Advocacy crime scene.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: That race is finally over, and the healing process can finally begin.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: You know you love a sport when you see a race that bad and you're still willing to watch it ever again.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: I haven't witnessed a finish that dissapointing since my first date with Rashida Collins.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: We can't all be racers I guess.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Maybe do a hard reset before it saves.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: The call it a qualifier, but after watching that dissapointing performance it is looking like almost none of these pilots are in fact qualified.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And an abyssmal race comes to an abyssmal end, absolutely ruining all of our lives.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: As another race day winds down, I hope you all had as much fun as I did. See you soon, racefans.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: A pleasure as always race fans. Goodbye and keep flying.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And that's all we have for today. Trevor Basque from New Horizon raceway signing off.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: With that, ladies, gentlemen, but mostly the ladies, this is Trevor Basque. Bidding you a fond adieu.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: All kidding aside, thanks for watching. This is Trevor Basque. Take care racers.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And so we conclude another step in the immortal journey of man and machine. Another display of technical prowess and raw instinct. Another chance to watch stuff blow up. Good night.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: That will do it for me, Trevor Basque. See you next time.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Thanks for joining me at New Horizon. I'm Trevor Basque. Keep flying.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Another race over, and another paycheck for me, your announcer Trevor Basque. Keep flying and good night.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And with that, today's qualifier comes to a close. I've been Trevor Basque. See you next time.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Shields are lighting up as some serious damage is dealt.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Nothing motivates a pilot to go a little faster better than getting shot at.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: And a pilot getting completely edged out of this fight. They may not have the muscle for it.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: I can say from experience, when you're getting shot like that, the main thing running through your head is, "Please don't hit my thrusters."

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Taking damage like this is not something any pilot can afford.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Advice to the pilots getting shot at, stop getting shot at.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: They are really getting torn up out there.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Many people focus on hull integrity while getting shot, but they shouldn't forget each impact is like applying a little tiny brake.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Maybe start avoiding the incoming fire? Just an idea.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You gotta mark a target, kid.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: That Glaive's a recognised Ace, enemy designation is Tank. We're gonna have to work together to take it down.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: We got more hostiles inbound. Looks like there's a a recognised Ace in the mix.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Copy that. I got the other. Good luck.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You can lock multiple missiles at once, just don't get too trigger happy.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Stop screwing around and target the Glaive.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You're taking a lot of hull damage. Try and keep a shield between you and the enemy.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: We're clear. Hell of a training session, huh.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You're cleared to engage the rest. Good luck.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Hold on, I've got contacts inbound

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: This is not a drill. I repeat, this is not a drill. All your systems are active. This is a live-fire encounter.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Stay sharp. We got more hostiles inbound. Looks like there's a Glaive in the mix.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Ease up. Your weapons are getting hot.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Fire in controlled bursts and give your weapons time to cool or they'll overheat.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Topped off. Let's get back out there.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Let's get you back to base. First round's on me.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You can also use it to overpower you manoeuvring thrusters in order to take tighter corners.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: If you need to get up to top speed in a hurry, try boosting.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You do have a limited amount that takes time to replenish, so don't go nuts with it.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You also have COMSTAB which adjusts your forward velocity so you can make controlled turns. Disabling COMSTAB will allow you maintain your velocity in turns, but you will drift wider..

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Still with me, kid? Good job. Now one thing you need to understand, every ship's outfitted with systems to look out for you.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: That last sharp turn you probably felt your ship clamp down on the turn. That's your G-Safe system kicking in, making sure that you aren't taking too many G-forces and blacking out.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: If you need to get that extra edge in turning, you can disable G-Safe, but be warned. An unconscious pilot turns into a dead one pretty quick.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Think you can put all this together? Let's see.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: If you need to cut speed in a hurry, use your space brake - it's much quicker than dialing back your engines and the moment you let go of it you'll automatically accelerate back up to your previous speed.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: That, my friend, is the Spire. Isn't she a beauty?

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Okay, that's enough. I don't think you're ready yet.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Think you can stay on my tail?

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: I'm getting erratic power spikes from your ship. They must have hit your power plant!

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Your ship's loaded with military intel, so we can't let it fall into enemy hands. You'll have to initiate self-destruct before you eject.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Rolling is a great way to orient your ship to fit through tight gaps or evade incoming fire. Now you give it a go.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Moving on. Now this is my favourite part of training: the Axial Roll.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Rolling is a great way to orient your ship to fit through tight gaps or evade incoming fire. Now you give it a go.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Moving on. Now this is my favourite part of training: the barrel roll.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: When pursuing a target, you'll want to keep your speed as close to their as possible. Give it a shot. Make sure I'm targeted and hit Match Speed.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Remember, this isn't autopilot, so you still have to steer, but you'll notice that once you're locked, your computer will continue to monitor my speed and adjust. It doesn't matter if I speed up slowly...

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Well, you seem to be able handle your ship, so let's see if you can handle a bit of combat.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: I've just enabled your targeting system. Use it to target me.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: If the Drone gets behind you, enter Decoupled mode to disengage your main engines and allow you to spin your ship around while retaining your original vector.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Give it a try, just remember to disengage it when you're done.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: It's a great way to dissuade a pursuer, but make sure you've checked your path ahead first.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Don't worry - it's just a training drone. It handles just like the real thing, but it's weapons are less lethal. Saying that - they still pack a punch so try not to take any hits you don't have to.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Good kill. We're heading back to the landing pad to restock and refuel for the final part of your training.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Its shields are down. Finish it off with a missile.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Let's move on - uh-oh! Looks like he had a friend. Take a look in your rear-view camera.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You're taking hits. Check your HUD for shield and damage status.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Good shot. See its shields weakening on your HUD?

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: That hit took out your weapons. You'll have to hold out until they come back online. Countermeasures are still online. Use them.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Deploying chaff takes more skill than flares. To be successful, you need to put it between you and the missile.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Good. Now, a chaff creates a cloud of electromagnetic interference to mask your signature from the missile.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: He's switched to EM tracking missiles. Cycle to chaff.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Flares have a short lifetime, don't be too quick to fire them.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Last missile was heat-seeking so equip your flares. Helpful tip, don't boost after dropping a flare. Boosted thrusters are much hotter than a flare.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You got your guns back, but I'll need more time to get your missiles up.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You got your missiles back. Take it out.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Missile locking sensors are on the nose so keep your target in front of you long enough to lock on.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Another pro tip: countermeasures are fired backward so never fly at a missile head-on, launch a countermeasure and expect it to work.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Check your radar. You should have a contact.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: There you go. Keep on the pressure.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Okay, try targetting the ship with the PIPs.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Notice you have multiple PIPs with varying lag? Each of those indicates a weapon on your ship. The computer's trying to compensate for the varying speeds between your ballistic and energy projectiles.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Now you have a target, you will have extra aim reticules. Those are Predicted-Impact-Points or PIPs. They'll show you where to shoot to hit a moving target.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Don't lose it. Stay on its tail.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Use your targeting system to quickly target the closest enemy.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Use your targeting system to target the closest enemy.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Okay, now look at the top right of your HUD. You should see you target displayed. This will show realtime damage, shield status and a few other things.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Shields are drawn as panels floating around the ship. They'll shrink as they weaken until they disappear completely. At that point, your shots will hit the hull and cause lasting damage.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Line up your target and fire when you're ready.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: I'm Lucas Baramsco, but everyone knows me as Gilly. I've served in six squadrons and qualified on almost a dozen ships, so if you put in the time, I'll get you on the path to dogfighting with the best of them.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: We're gonna set you up in the ship on the landing pad to your right. Hustle over and let's get going.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: We're gonna set you up in the FC7 on the landing pad over there. Hustle over and let's get going.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Don't think you can slink your way through this. You need to focus and execute my commands because there is zero room for error in the black. We clear?

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You can use the automatic EDL landing procedure or do the whole thing manually.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Remember, entering Landing Mode will automatically Decouple your ship, so don't activate it too far away from the landing pad as it cuts down your speed.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Remember, entering Landing Mode will automatically Decouple your ship, so don't activate it too far away from the landing pad as it cuts down your speed.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: The flight system automatically cuts down on your speed when you deploy the landing gear, so don't activate it too far away from the landing pad.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: If you raise you landing gear or stray too far from the pad, you'll have to request it again.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: To enter landing mode you need to lower your landing gear.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Once Landing Mode's active, your HUD's going to swap out your combat systems for landing specific functionality..

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Free landing pads will appear on your HUD.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Your radar is replaced by the landing system. It'll guide you to your landing pad and help you perform a safe landing.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Make sure your ship stays within the bounds of the pad and keep your eye on your pitch and roll.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Once you've targeted a landing pad, request permission to land.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You can cycle through available landing pads the same as cycling through targets.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Go ahead and pick a landing pad.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: In there you'll see your weapon groups, shield configuration and power distribution.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: While we're waiting, feel free to take a look at your ship's setup.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: I wouldn't mess around with them during training.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You'll notice the majority of your systems are disabled. I'll be controlling when they are on and offline to simulate potential scenarios in combat situations.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Alright. First thing's first, take a look around your cockpit and familiarise yourself with the layout. It's imperative to quickly find and access specific controls. Last thing you want to be doing in a scrap is bringing up the instructions.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Let's get ready for takeoff. I'll do this step by step to show you how it's done. Look over at me and watch what I do.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Activating landing mode restricts you to decoupled mode, meaning only your manoeuvring thrusters fire, which is handy for precise movement in tight areas.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Activating landing mode restricts you to decoupled mode, meaning only your manoeuvring thrusters fire, which is handy for precise movement in tight areas.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: I've gone ahead and restricted you to decoupled mode, which makes it much easier to position yourself for a launch. In Decoupled Mode, your main engine is disengaged, allowing you to move more precisely using your manoeuvring thrusters.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Once you're aligned, the tower will open the doors.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Take note that you're in take-off and landing mode..

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: That's it. Once I clear out, it'll be your turn.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Make sure you don't pitch or roll. It'll be tough to get back into proper alignment.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Ready? I'm enabling your systems and will monitor your progress from up here.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: The tower will open the doors once you're lined up.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Great job. I haven't seen many pull one off on the first try.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Don't align yourself with the middle of the doors. You'd be surprised how many 'cruits forget that the cockpit is not the centre of the ship.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Okay. Now strafe forward onto the taxiway. If you need it, the tower should have lit up your path.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Nice, you're clear of the pad.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Don't turn too much. You don't want to fall out of alignment.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Now that I'm clear I can strafe forward onto the taxiway.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Now I square my ship up with the ceiling doors ready for a vertical take-off.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Alright, first I want to lift vertically until I'm just clear of the landing pad.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Not bad. You'll get the hang of it.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: <sigh> That needs a lot of work.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: What are you waiting for? Go finish it off.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Let's go. You're on the clock, rookie.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: I can't let you eject without initiating self-destruct.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: It's the only thing I can't do it remotely, kid. You have to initiate. Hurry.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Your plant's leaking radiation. You need to self-destruct now.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: This kind of hesitation can get you killed. Fire.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Go ahead, shoot. The drone isn't going to mind.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Ah, don't sweat it, everybody tags their ship the first time. Your ship is still spaceworthy so I we'll just press on.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: What are you, on break? Let's move it, rook.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Move it, move it, move it.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Let's move it, rookie. You aren't getting paid by the hour.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: We're on a clock here, let's go.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You could use some extra hours in the sim, but you weren't too bad back there.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You did good back there, kid. Let me guess - you're an Arena Commander fan?

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: I know it's your first time out there, but you're going to have to try harder if you want your wings.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Easy there, rookie. That's my ride.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: What are you doing? You're over there.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: What the hell's wrong with you?

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Still with me? Alright, I'm a little impressed.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: I don't have time for this.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Come on. You can do better than that.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Let's go, let's go. I'm falling asleep up here.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Keep up, kid, you're blowing it.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You gonna give up now? Come on, push yourself.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Turn around. I won't say it again.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Stay focused. Let's get through this.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Let's get back on track. We got a lot to cover.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Just so we're clear, kid: you will follow orders or you will fail this training exercise.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Sharpen up, rookie. This isn't going to cut it.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: You reading me? What the hell's wrong with you?

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: A little shaky, but vertical take-offs take some practice.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Let's head back. Guess you need more time in the sims.

dialogue.speaker: 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Yeah, I don't think your ship can take any more. I think we'll need to get it patched up and try again.

dialogue.speaker: 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512

dialogue.subtitleText:
We are drawn towards the familiar. It is safe, reliable.
But it can shackle us to the ordinary when in our souls we long to strike out and become something new.
We started with a simple match. Dare to dream. Dare to challenge the expectations of what has come before.
To embrace the Unique, to put everything on the line.
Only when we risk everything can we discover something truly special, and redefine what it means to drive with the stars.
To explore the farthest reaches, to race on the cutting edge, to Protect what you love.
Say goodbye to the familiar, and welcome the brand new Mustang, where risk, meets reward.

dialogue.speaker: 33cb9aa3-418c-48d8-b887-c3803b44df72
dialogue.subtitleText:
Space, the best ships gracefully dance across its expense, the worst clumsily plod across its face. The new M50 doesnt have time for any of that.
Instead, it simply slices its way through.The 2944 M50 was designed with one goal in mind: Make the ship that will win the next Murray Cup.
The surprising thing is, Origin may have just about done it.
The stats are an orgy of mind-bending numbers but it comes down to two things. Less weight and more power. Youll notice the nose cone has grown what I can only describe as a mustache, added to stabilize all the additional thrust that the retooled and updated Twin Hammer HM4point3 drives spew out. And the refinement doesnt stop there.
They ve narrowed the front fuselage, moved the wings forward for better balance, shaved the cockpit viewpane down to the finest it could still be and not shatter in your face.
The result. A pure flying machine. Each movement on the stick translates directly into unadulterated throttle action. Welcome back to the glory days of flying.
